app.title: Supplementary Materials
app.p: The supplementary data consist of the Figures S1–S21 and spectral data. Figure S1 showed GC-MS equipped with HP-5 ms, HP-1 and HP-INNOWax capillary columns TiC spectra for Lavender essential oil. Figures S2–S21 showed GC-EI-QTOF-MS Tic spectra, MS spectra and 13C spectra for compounds 9, 10, 12, 13, 17, 18, 19, 21, 27, 29, 32, 33, 38, 39, 40, 41, 43, 45, 46, 47.
